General.Name: Lubair Aviation Technology Co.Ltd.
General.Description: Lubair Aviation Technology Co., Ltd. engages in the distribution of civil aviation fuel, aviation raw materials, and aviation chemicals. It deals with brands, such as Exxon Mobil, 3M, EC, Lufthansa Technology, Huntsman, LANXESS, Bosch, and others. The company was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Shenzhen, China.
